Requirements:
    Twisted (Specifically Twisted Web)
    twitty-twister (included as a git submodule)

Installation:
    1. Clone this source code
    2. Make sure you have Twisted Web
    3. Run 'git submodule init', then 'git submodule update' to get the latest version of my twitty-twister fork
    4. Copy settings.py.example to settings.py and update the information in the file
    5. Run the bot with 'twist -oy bot.tac' ('twistd -noy bot.tac' to run in the foreground)

Credits:
    This code is based on the following projects

    1. PyAIML - http://pyaiml.sourceforge.net/
    2. Howie Bot - http://howie.sourceforge.net/
    3. Twitty Twister - http://github.com/dustin/twitty-twister/
    4. Twisted - http://twistedmatrix.com/

